msgid "desc_r_Gem Amethyst"
msgstr ""
"Amethyst has a violet or purple color, and is a popular gem often used in "
"jewelry. Can be used store an enchant up to 3.00 quality."

msgid "desc_r_Gem Aventurine"
msgstr ""
"A valuable stone with a soft shimmering effect. It is often used in making "
"jewelry. Can be used store an enchant up to 2.00 quality."

msgid "desc_r_Gem Crystal"
msgstr ""
"Fairly common as far as precious stones go, and can often be found adorning "
"commoner's jewelry and the cheaper magestaffs. Can be used store an enchant "
"of 1.00 quality."

msgid "desc_r_Gem Diamond"
msgstr ""
"A treasured stone, used when making the finest jewelry. Can be used store an "
"enchant up to 5.00 quality."

msgid "desc_r_Gem Emerald"
msgstr ""
"A rare and valuable gemstone with a fine green colour. It is said to ward "
"off evil spirits, and often adorn holy symbols. Can be used store an enchant "
"up to 4.00 quality."

msgid "desc_r_Gem Fire Aegis"
msgstr " "

