"Can be used store an enchant up to 3.00 quality."

msgid "desc_r_Gem Hades"
msgstr " "

msgid "desc_r_Gem Ruby"
msgstr ""
"A deep red colored and highly sought after gemstone. It symbolizes "
"passionate love, and is very popular among noblewomen. Can be used store an "
"enchant up to 4.00 quality."

msgid "desc_r_Gem Sapphire"
msgstr ""
"One of the rarest and most valuable gemstones on Agon. Can be used store an "
"enchant up to 5.00 quality."

